Title: Lieutenant Jangles
Actors: Matt Dickie, Justin Gerardin, Tamara McLaughlin, Daniel Mulhall
Plot: It's the mid 1980's in the most crime ridden city of Australia. Only one man keeps the scales of justice even. Cowboy Detective, Lieutenant Jangles. After his partner is killed in a blazing shootout, Jangles goes on an explosive and blood soaked mission to avenge his death. His quest for vengeance unintentionally makes him the enemy of a mysterious new crime boss, who has been quietly taking over...
